body.name: Dickies Men's Leather Double Prong Belt
features: UNIQUE DESIGN: If you are looking for a belt that reflects your outstanding personality, this double prong and double holes jeans belt might be the one. The unique design of this casual belt won’t let you go unnoticed.
100% LEATHER: Crafted from 100% leather, this high-quality leather belt gives you a nice and clean look with any looks. The sleek and smooth strap leather is perfect to finish off any of your outfit.
SIZING: For best fit, select belt size 2 inches larger than your pant size. For example, if your pant size is 34”, shop belt size 36”. Strap width 1 1/2".

DICKIES QUALITY: At Dickies we take pride in designing belts that are made for your everyday life. From work to family time we craft sturdy, yet fashionable belts that you can wear anytime and any wear. The buckle features a roller end with double prong.
body.description: This Double Prong Casual Belt from Dickies is sure to be your new everyday go-to. The sleek and timeless style is durable and meant to last. Featuring an english style tip shape and fully adjustable double prong style strap, this belt from Dickies will be your new favorite. Pair with Khakis, jeans or other pants to create an effortlessly cool and functional look. Since its beginnings in 1922, every piece of Dickies workwear has stood for the quality, toughness, and pride that embodies the spirit of the American worker.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice quality and look, holes the whole length
reviews.reviewText: I liked it better than expected. A timeless style, holes the whole length so it can accommodate my female body for years. Thick leather but not too thick and stiff. Good value purchase. I got it to use on a couple jeans that stretch out too much and start falling down after the first day of wear so I only wore them for yard and house work. But now I also wear them in town with this belt because it looks nice casual. This belt works equally well for men and women.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars tough and comfortable
reviews.reviewText: I'm a bigger guy and it's hard to find comfortable belts. But this I absolutely love I honestly forget I'm even wearing a belt. The holes make it easy to get get just the right fit which I normally can't. It's also very tough I've caught on things and my dog got hold of it chewed up it some but I still wear it it hasn't even tried to fall apart or break. For bigger guys this is a must

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This belt is thick but doesn’t feel it but also doesn’t feel too thin. Great belt, feels heavy duty. Good hardware.I like belts like this that are completely adjustable to double as tourniquets or straps to carry or drag people.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought this so I could do a look like the main character from the Michael Bay Texas chainsaw, massacre and it’s giving it works. It’s really nice I like that it has all the little holes around the belt. I bought it a little bit long so I could like tuck it and it’s cute.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 5.0 out of 5 stars Value priced, meets or exceeds description, works as advertised and is a value.
reviews.reviewText: I purchase several things on Amazon and was giving pretty in-depth reviews. From this point on, here's the new agenda…. if it works as advertised, is well made, meets or exceeds the description, is a value, and arrives in a fair amount of time, it will get a "star rating" equal to what my expectations were/are. If it doesn't meet these criteria, then I will most definitely and descriptively tell the short comings of the products and you as a consumer will not have to go through the trouble of buying the product without some background knowledge. If the sell pulls that item and relists under another description, I will put the exact same review on the seller's feedback page. Sellers have done this a couple of times in the past, and I was true to my word then as well as now. DR
